#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:1
msgid "Meson package"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:6
msgid "A Meson package provides support for processing a [Meson][meson] supported module."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:13
msgid "During the configuration stage of a Meson package, `meson setup` will be invoked to generate build files for the module. For the build stage, `meson compile` will invoke the generated build files. For the installation stage (if enabled), `meson install` will be used. Each stage can be configured to manipulate environment variables and options used by Meson."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:19
msgid "The default configuration built for projects is `debugoptimized`. A developer can override this option by explicitly adjusting the configuration option `LIBFOO_MESON_BUILD_TYPE` to, for example, `debug`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:27
msgid "The following shows the default arguments used in stages and outlines configuration options that are available for a Meson package to set. See also the [Meson package examples](/examples/examples-meson). All stages are invoked with a [`PKG_BUILD_DIR`](env-pkg-build-dir) working directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:37
msgid "Configuration stage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:40
msgid "The configuration stage invokes `meson` with the arguments:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:53
msgid "The build type is configured by [`LIBFOO_MESON_BUILD_TYPE`](pkg-opt-meson-build-type)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:56
msgid "The build output directory is configured to [`PKG_BUILD_OUTPUT_DIR`](env-pkg-build-output-dir)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:59
msgid "Paths may vary based on how the package's [`LIBFOO_INSTALL_TYPE`](pkg-opt-install-type) is configured. System root paths provided will only include the staging directory if `staging` is configured. Both the staging and target directories are provided is the `target` is configured. Likewise with the host directory if `host` is configured. pkg-config paths are defined to `<sysroot>/lib/pkgconfig`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:66
msgid "If [`LIBFOO_PREFIX`](pkg-opt-prefix) resolves to an empty prefix, the `-Dprefix` define is not provided."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:69
msgid "In the event that a package is reconfigured (e.g. [`<pkg>-reconfigure`](action-pkg-reconfigure)), the `--reconfigure` argument will also be included."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:79
msgid "Build stage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:82
msgid "The build stage invokes `meson` with the arguments:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:88
#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:117
msgid "The `-C` directory is configured to [`PKG_BUILD_OUTPUT_DIR`](env-pkg-build-output-dir)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:91
msgid "The number of jobs is populated by either the [`--jobs` argument](arg-jobs), [`LIBFOO_FIXED_JOBS`](pkg-opt-fixed-jobs) or [`LIBFOO_MAX_JOBS`](pkg-opt-max-jobs). Although, if the configuration results in a single job, the argument will not be used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:102
msgid "Install stage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:105
msgid "The install stage invokes `meson` with the arguments:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:111
msgid "With the following environment variables set:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:120
msgid "The `--destdir` argument and `DESTDIR` environment path will be set to the target sysroot the package should install into (see also [`LIBFOO_INSTALL_TYPE`](pkg-opt-install-type)). `meson install` may be invoked multiple times for each target it needs to install into."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-meson.md:125
msgid "The installation stage can be skipped by configuring [`LIBFOO_MESON_NOINSTALL`](pkg-opt-meson-noinstall)."
msgstr ""

